{
  "stem": "3605.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, just by the names was a signal of hope.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And since those young people didn't have any school, not only did we provide them with education in groups-- because our group of 50 people was teaching [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 500 children.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Each of us was teaching 10 or 12, or depending [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-- in the age group or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But not only did we teach those 12-year-olds, but we were-- we were supplying them with a spiritual outlet and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they also met in our garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The oldest group didn't meet in our garden, just our group and those younger people that we organized.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had a self help if one of our members got sick or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The produce from the garden were used mainly to support our sick members.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A lot of them had TB.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the situation was very, very rough in the ghetto, due to the fact that they weren't giving us any rations.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People were starving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You could find swollen people from hunger on the street, and it was just starting to get hopeless, the situation with the great hunger.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to begin with there were 15,000, 12,000.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, there were 20,000 because from surrounding towns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And 25.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were all very much bunched up and gathered together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the hygienic circumstances weren't so great.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as a result, a lot of sickness and typhus was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you have 10, 15 people living in an apartment that doesn't have toilet facilities and doesn't have a wash room, at best, as you know it here in America, you bring up the water to wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
